ailab is packaged as a Python application using Debian's pybuild workflow.

The package depends on snapd and installs the lxd snap from its post-install
script because Debian package dependencies cannot target an individual snap.

After installing the package, initialize LXD if needed:

  sudo lxd init --auto

Then add your user to the lxd group and re-login:

  sudo usermod -aG lxd $USER
